## Common Mistakes to Avoid

### ❌ Don't

```typescript
// ❌ Using 'any'
const fetchData = async (): Promise<any> => { ... }

// ❌ No error handling
const { data } = await supabase.from('transactions').select('*');

// ❌ localStorage
localStorage.setItem('filters', JSON.stringify(filters));

// ❌ Adding currency column (Phase 1)
ALTER TABLE transactions ADD COLUMN currency TEXT;

// ❌ Suggesting Phase 2+ features without checking
"Let's add vendor master table..." // Check PHASE.md first!
```

### ✅ Do

```typescript
// ✅ Explicit types
const fetchTransactions = async (): Promise<Transaction[]> => { ... }

// ✅ Error handling
try {
  const { data, error } = await supabase.from('transactions').select('*');
  if (error) throw error;
  return data;
} catch (error) {
  console.error('Failed to fetch:', error);
  throw error;
}

// ✅ Check phase before suggesting
"This feature requires Phase 2 (vendor master). 
Current phase is 1. Defer or propose phase upgrade?"
```

